N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7920.11 - Rescission, withholding, and adjustment of program rebates

State Regulations

The Energy Office, in addition to any other rights and
remedies it may have pursuant to law, may withhold, rescind, or adjust payment
of a program rebate or any portion thereof for failure to comply with the
requirements of this Part or the terms and conditions of the notice of rebate
commitment. Notes
